{"tid":1788391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登道德撚入嚟，我原諒達哥、ming 仔","createTime":"2019-12-18T15:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T16:00:53.000Z","uid":87915,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"039e55bf34a65c43828eb59e827a4e87c86e21e1","tid":1788391,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"為咗黃色經濟圈，我不惜將自己原則 底線降低<br />\n<br />\n只要冇講過任何撐警  支持政府  我當佢冇表態  唔屌<br />\n<br />\n今時今日  咁遲先來講支持示威者，我就支持<br />\n<br />\n達哥  ming 仔  黃子華  我今日係唔會再屌<br />\n<br />\n本身話支持警察，去到今日話支持示威者我都冇問題，不過持觀望態度<br />\n<br />\n只要講一句就得，唔使捐錢，唔使出力，最緊要表態。因為時間會證明一切<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己圍內都搞唔掂，仲喺度分化，你哋對唔對得住手足"},{"pid":"64a34994e5d761653a6a0848221a8aff27f4870d","tid":1788391,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:30:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39039a9e1534991cb68e51c264eb78f36f29d2db","tid":1788391,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"係兄弟就明"},{"pid":"10d4e19d639e07b057af73ac7f3ddbb8d374f70d","tid":1788391,"uid":49336,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAJw4kO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAJw4kO.gif&h=d8cc8715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Po90XFD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPo90XFD.jpg&h=50404781&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31d0dd90df81a0bfd17c6d9fed429e1fecd30082","tid":1788391,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:43:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c8371663338642963154b579cceb238e295601c","tid":1788391,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T16:00:53.000Z","msg":"推"}]}